data.oai_dc:dc: These data were collected from 2003-2014 at East Bay Island, Southampton Island, Nunavut, Canada. These are data from pre-recruiting, wild-living female common eiders with metrics collected at arrival on the breeding grounds, reproductive outputs, and physiological fattening measured in the lab.
